{"tid":164071,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有啲咩人/組合 如果係外國嘅話一早就紅咗？","createTime":"2017-03-20T12:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T16:33:31.000Z","uid":29601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb7b54d9a1fb89f318c812833a05d132f9cdb22","tid":164071,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"紅嘅定義係有外國媒體會報導下你咁<br />\n類似曹星如咁 不過曹星如喺香港都已經紅咗所以唔符合標題 <br />\n<br />\n類型不限 作家、導演、畫家、樂隊、作曲家、運動員、政治人物、教授、演員、藝人、廚師、youtuber、實況主、gamer、攝影師、model etc.<br />\n自己暫時諗唔到 大家可唔可以舉啲例子 想見識多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a391dabdc99cef66b5060d7f3d337ab51d7bf7","tid":164071,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"達哥真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf47e28683ca05b7019ac47161109038d07cb4b","tid":164071,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"c94722bf4ecff826d498f8d1027d9b1496c0efb8","tid":164071,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4271f91a1b74feb02f8291044597c28ff82aa7be","tid":164071,"uid":92383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"羅莽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4bc6a7286d165dfdd3e0f0b283471e1bade789","tid":164071,"uid":80549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"郭偉亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327c405df116d99bea441a3d0084e3060c857904","tid":164071,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>達哥真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"4cd47ab39e9a76eb23c732cc854481ee249f4533","tid":164071,"uid":296